title: Out now: ‘Most wanted’ by Jazzy B featuring Snoop Dogg and Mr. Capone-E
text:
Jazzy B's much-awaited track, 'Most wanted' is here and it is totally worth the wait.
Jazzy B, who has been in the music industry for about 24 years, has proved that it is not without a reason that he is called the Crown Prince of Bhangra. He has delivered a number of hits, with the latest one being 'Mitran de boot' , for which he collaborated with Kaur B.
Another artist who features in 'Most wanted' is Snoop Dogg. Known as one of the pioneers of rap music, Snoop rose to fame in India with his rap in the title song of Akshay Kumar's Singh Is Kinng . And now, the rapper has collaborated with a Punjabi artist, which is a combination you rarely get to see.
The song also showcases Mr. Capone-E, a Pakistani-American rapper who has enjoyed success with the track 'Don't get it twisted' .
Source: Simplybhangra.com
